Write a program to demonstrate usage of  functions , passing list as argument , recursion, local and global scope using  in Python

x = "global"

def foo():
    print("x inside:", x)


foo()
print("x outside:", x)

Output:-
x inside: global
x outside: global



def foo():
    y = "local"
    print(y)

foo()

Output:-
Local

x = "global "

def foo():
    global x
    y = "local"
    x = x * 2
    print(x)
    print(y)

foo()

Output:-

global global 
local
